eakness is that HKMA does not have infinite USD on hand."},{"pid":"631bb9d3d30e32f9798cf3ab9696ce234a68d0d1","tid":1475647,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"你個問題問得好，令我都諗深一層覺得會失敗<br />\n<br />\n1:提港幣現金係為左達到擠提效果<br />\n2:兌美金係為左動搖聯繫匯率<br />\n<br />\n兌美金即係將港幣放返入銀行，變相幫1補血<br />\n而美金係世界上流通量最大既貨幣，政府或者銀行都極容易係海外調動/借到現鈔返黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係依家有2個杯麵，如果想見到個杯底，一係將2個杯面食哂，一係淨係食其中一個，依家2個都食極大機會最終2個杯麵都食淨<br />\n<br />\n失敗後，d人無可能將d錢放入枕頭底，都係放返入銀行，之後成個金融體系回返血"},{"pid":"14ba692f72c2f9210c767f43e8cb643613c47e26","tid":1475647,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:20:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">道歉，係因為阻住咗人。<br />\n道歉，係展示我哋嘅人民質素。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">文宣道歉，希望保護過家園的你地明白我們的困境。<br />\n已包埋內地嘅示威活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNcr1bW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNcr1bW.jpg&h=2fdc1bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n借多個位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVtrfTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVtrfTe.jpg&h=32eb9a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNJVTES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNJVTES.jpg&h=070ec636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuBgC6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuBgC6v.jpg&h=4e21a231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EesWC6u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEesWC6u.jpg&h=4d3f45a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<